msgstr "Dull mewnbwn"

#: usr/lib/linuxmint/mintLocale/mintLocale.py:313
msgid ""
"Input methods are used to write symbols and characters which are not present "
"on the keyboard. They are useful to write in Chinese, Japanese, Korean, "
"Thai, Vietnamese..."
msgstr ""
"Mae dull mewnbwn yn cael ei ddefnyddio i ysgrifennu symbolau a nodau sydd "
"ddim ar gael ar y bysellfwrdd. Maen nhw'n ddefnyddiol ar gyfer ysgrifennu "
"Tsieinëeg, Japanëeg, Corëeg, Thai a Fietnamëeg..."

